{"tid":285613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同果班抵位許業行既人講返肺苦之言","createTime":"2017-06-16T03:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T04:02:28.000Z","uid":54747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c19b6750df8342ffca0f447d387f7a4878c4d58","tid":285613,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到早洩到今時今日都仲係咁不知悔改<br />\n向到縱容你班手下胡作非為<br />\n<br />\n我地黎得LIHKG<br />\n一早係將自己身家性命交託左比連巴<br />\n我地絕對相信連巴唔似得早洩咁卑鄙無恥<br />\n<br />\n老老實實  如果你肯一早為BAM HKG+而公開地躹躬道歉<br />\n根本就唔會搞到今時今日咁樣既局面<br />\n<br />\n到左今日高登再無高登仔係閣下咎由自取<br />\n你以為打殘LIHKG我地就會返返去你個垃圾高登只係你夢心妄想<br />\n<br />\n2016年11月出得第一個LIHKG  <br />\n我地就有本事可以再出得到千千萬萬個LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多都無謂<br />\n我地對連尼住同望遠兩位巴打係無條件信任<br />\n當中既情義係你依啲反覆無常既小人唔會明白<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之一句到尾<br />\n我就點都撐LIHKG</blockquote>"},{"pid":"96e144e945e6e2bee65c23a1d54bd59898d8363b","tid":285613,"uid":106422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07738227c17a253e907f0e3f9c7a53606091c931","tid":285613,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:41:04.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"54553781e8e1f2f3f03ea46a65bba4e77ed637a5","tid":285613,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"🤘"},{"pid":"0fbd3e0dd0ce241993b065c096cc48318e3a6715","tid":285613,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:58:07.000Z","msg":"睇到咸左😭"},{"pid":"9a8af720dcff9eebbc4fcabe24d396b785784928","tid":285613,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"連神😭"}]}